274
00:17:04,278 --> 00:17:07,078
Nagisa must've panicked.

275
00:17:08,578 --> 00:17:10,578
Calm down, Nagisa.

276
00:17:11,678 --> 00:17:13,778
We have three more minutes.

277
00:17:19,278 --> 00:17:21,578
We need to film the real thing.

278
00:17:23,078 --> 00:17:25,678
You're late, Yuri.

279
00:17:25,678 --> 00:17:27,378
She won't make it in time.

280
00:17:29,778 --> 00:17:33,478
Yuri! I'm glad you made it.

