290
00:18:39,678 --> 00:18:44,278
At the studio, the stand-in maid stabbed Red Hood to death.

291
00:18:44,278 --> 00:18:47,478
All that remained was Nagisa's final shot.

292
00:18:49,078 --> 00:18:52,478
Nagisa, the real jewel won't make it in time.

293
00:18:52,478 --> 00:18:56,978
I'm sorry, but you'll have to wear the fake ring.

294
00:18:56,978 --> 00:18:58,878
I... I understand.

295
00:19:05,278 --> 00:19:07,678
I...

296
00:19:12,978 --> 00:19:14,378
I...

