302
00:19:44,978 --> 00:19:49,678
And Nagisa's current condition, but...

303
00:19:49,678 --> 00:19:53,078
It's too bad that it's only speculation.

304
00:19:53,078 --> 00:19:54,678
It can't be helped.

305
00:19:54,678 --> 00:19:57,778
Hey, didn't you say

