00:20:21,378 --> 00:20:26,678
I saw something shining when you showed us this film

315
00:20:26,678 --> 00:20:29,478
on the editor this afternoon.

316
00:20:33,078 --> 00:20:36,078
Just before the words "The End" appear onscreen,

317
00:20:36,078 --> 00:20:39,978
